abstract: Fox’s crime drama “Bones” delivered solid ratings with its fourth-season premiere on Wednesday.
snippet: Fox’s crime drama “Bones” delivered solid ratings with its fourth-season premiere on Wednesday.
lead_paragraph: Fox’s crime drama “Bones” delivered solid ratings with its fourth-season premiere on Wednesday, earning 9.7 million viewers from 8 to 10 p.m., according to Nielsen’s estimates. It was the show’s best season debut since its first episode, in 2005.
